7b/SarahSharples.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-21T09:30:10.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Professor Sarah Sharples has been appointed to the Council that advises the Prime Minister and Cabinet on science and technology.</p>\n</div>","title":"Professor Sarah Sharples appointed to the Council for Science and Technology"},{"document_type":"Correspondence","href":"/government/publications/photonics-capturing-the-opportunities-for-growth-and-global-leadership","image":{"alt_text":"Close-up image of fibre‑optic strands fanning outward, emitting points of blue light against a dark background.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69aea1cc671a8a924c83ee81/s712_AdobeStock_254953141.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69aea1ccbde9c3f213c899b1/s465_AdobeStock_254953141.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69aea1ccd620c14fa183ee84/AdobeStock_254953141.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-09T09:30:04.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Advice to the Prime Minister on how the UK can achieve growth and global leadership in the photonics sector.</p>\n</div>","title":"Photonics: capturing the opportunities for growth and global leadership"},{"document_type":"Correspondence","href":"/government/publications/letter-to-the-prime-minister-on-climate-adaptation-and-resilience","image":{"alt_text":"Image of a sustainable city model generated with AI","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694198141ec67214e98f303e/s712_AdobeStock_1713836784.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69419814f065108822537585/s465_AdobeStock_1713836784.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6941981458a21370f58f304f/AdobeStock_1713836784.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-01T09:30:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Advice to the Prime Minister on the importance of climate adaptatio